fields.request: Manual QA: Confirm OCPP EV admin screens work after model relocation
fields.request_details:
Visit the OCPP EV admin sections and ensure the pages render without errors.
1. Open /admin/ocpp/brand/ and verify existing brands display correctly.
2. Create a temporary brand with a WMI code, then delete it after confirming the change history records the operation.
3. Open /admin/ocpp/evmodel/ and /admin/ocpp/electricvehicle/ to confirm the inlines and search filters operate as before.
